us.php] |- | [[Claude Bernard University Lyon 1|Université Claude Bernard]] | 4,000,000 | LY | France; [[Lyon]] | [http://herbier.univ-lyon1.fr/] |- | [[Joint Herbarium of the University of Zurich and the ETH Zurich]] | 3,500,000 | Z+ZT | Switzerland, [[Zurich]] | [http://www.zuerich-herbarien.ethz.ch] |- | [[Botanic Garden Meise]] | 3,500,000 | BR | Belgium, [[Meise]] | [http://www.plantentuinmeise.be/RESEARCH/COLLECTIONS/HERBARIUM/herbariumdescription.php] |- | [[Botanical Garden in Berlin|Botanischer Garten und Botanisches Museum Berlin-Dahlem]],<br/>Zentraleinrichtung der Freien Universität Berlin | 3,000,000 | B | Germany, [[Berlin]] | [http://www.bgbm.org/BGBM/research/colls/herb/default.htm] |- | [[Finnish Museum of Natural History]] ([[University of Helsinki]]) | 3,000,000 | H | [[Finland]], [[Helsinki]] | [https://web.archive.org/web/20080615004626/http://www.fmnh.helsinki.fi/english/botany/index.htm] |- | [[Botanische Staatssammlung München]] | 3,000,000 | M | Germany, [[Munich]] | [http://www.botanischestaatssammlung.de/] |- | [[University of Copenhagen]] | 2,510,000 | C | Denmark, [[Copenhagen]] | [http://botanik.snm.ku.dk/Samlinger/Herbarier/] |- |[[Hungarian Natural History Museum]] - Department of Botany | 2,000,000 | BP | [[Budapest, Hungary]] | [http://www.nhmus.hu/en/collections/department_of_botany] |- | [[Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh|Royal Botanic Garden, Edinburgh]] | 2,000,000 | E | [[United Kingdom|UK]]; [[Edinburgh]], Scotland | [http://www.rbge.org.uk/science/herbarium] |- | Herbarium Hamburgense | 1,800,000 | HBG | Germany, [[Hamburg]] | [http://www.herbariumhamburgense.de] |- | [[Senckenberg Research Institute]], Frankfurt | 1,200,000 | FR | Germany, [[Frankfurt]] | [http://www.senckenberg.de/root/index.php?page_id=823] |- | [[Moscow State University]] (Московский государственный университет) | 1,011,253 | MW | Russia; [[Moscow]] | [https://plant.mitotech.ru/], [https://plant.mitotech.ru/] |- | [[University of Cambridge]] | 1,000,000 | C